works.description: Forget the high-tech luxury coffee tables for a while, and take a look at this amazing table from the house of Duffy London. Dubbed the Woodsman Axe, this coffee table is sure a conversation starter with its axe-y bold looks. Designed by Chris Duffy and inspired by the Brothers Grimm fairy tale “Little Red Riding Hood,” the Woodsman Axe Coffee Table is one heck of a minimalist yet bold coffee table I’ve ever seen.
